      <title>MarkDownLearning</title>
      <link href="/2022/10/08/MarkDownLearning/"/>
      <url>/2022/10/08/MarkDownLearning/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="This-is-a-code-for-learning-MarkDown-Grammar"><a href="#This-is-a-code-for-learning-MarkDown-Grammar" class="headerlink" title="This is a code for learning MarkDown Grammar."></a>This is a code for learning MarkDown Grammar.</h1><span id="more"></span><h2 id="Title-Grammar"><a href="#Title-Grammar" class="headerlink" title="Title Grammar"></a>Title Grammar</h2><h2 id="标题语法"><a href="#标题语法" class="headerlink" title="标题语法"></a>标题语法</h2><blockquote><h1 id="Level-1"><a href="#Level-1" class="headerlink" title="Level 1"></a>Level 1</h1><h2 id="Level-2"><a href="#Level-2" class="headerlink" title="Level 2"></a>Level 2</h2><h3 id="Level-3"><a href="#Level-3" class="headerlink" title="Level 3"></a>Level 3</h3><h4 id="Level-4"><a href="#Level-4" class="headerlink" title="Level 4"></a>Level 4</h4><h5 id="Level-5"><a href="#Level-5" class="headerlink" title="Level 5"></a>Level 5</h5><h6 id="Level-6"><a href="#Level-6" class="headerlink" title="Level 6"></a>Level 6</h6></blockquote><h2 id="Paragapha-Grammar"><a href="#Paragapha-Grammar" class="headerlink" title="Paragapha Grammar"></a>Paragapha Grammar</h2><h2 id="段落语法"><a href="#段落语法" class="headerlink" title="段落语法"></a>段落语法</h2><blockquote><p>Don’t put tabs or spaces in front of your  paragraphs.</p><p>Keep lines left-aligned like this.</p></blockquote><h2 id="Line-Break"><a href="#Line-Break" class="headerlink" title="Line Break"></a>Line Break</h2><h2 id="换行"><a href="#换行" class="headerlink" title="换行"></a>换行</h2><blockquote><p>This is the first line.<br>句尾添加两个空格加回车即可进行换行<br>And this the second line.</p></blockquote><h2 id="Bold"><a href="#Bold" class="headerlink" title="Bold"></a>Bold</h2><h2 id="粗体"><a href="#粗体" class="headerlink" title="粗体"></a>粗体</h2><blockquote><p>This is <strong>Bold</strong>.</p></blockquote><h2 id="Italic"><a href="#Italic" class="headerlink" title="Italic"></a>Italic</h2><blockquote><p>This is <em>Italic</em>.<br>This is <em><strong>Bold Italic</strong></em>.</p></blockquote><h2 id="引用块语法"><a href="#引用块语法" class="headerlink" title="引用块语法"></a>引用块语法</h2><blockquote><p> <strong>The quarterly results look great!</strong></p><ul><li>Revenue was off the chart.</li><li>Profits were higher than ever.</li></ul><p> <em>Everything</em> is going according to <strong>plan</strong>.</p></blockquote><h2 id="列表语法（有序列表和无序列表）"><a href="#列表语法（有序列表和无序列表）" class="headerlink" title="列表语法（有序列表和无序列表）"></a>列表语法（有序列表和无序列表）</h2><h3 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a>有序列表</h3><ol><li>first item  </li><li>second item<br> Paragapha <em>insert</em><blockquote><p>引用块  </p></blockquote></li><li>third item</li></ol><h3 id="无序列表"><a href="#无序列表" class="headerlink" title="无序列表"></a>无序列表</h3><ul><li><p>first item</p><p>  insert code block</p><pre><code>  &lt;html&gt;      &lt;head&gt;          &lt;title&gt;Test&lt;/title&gt;      &lt;/head&gt;</code></pre></li><li><p>second item</p><blockquote><p>define block</p></blockquote><p>  insert image block</p><p>  <img src="/2022/10/08/MarkDownLearning/farmer.png" alt="image,famer"></p></li><li><p>third item</p><p>  list block insert</p><ul><li>first block</li><li>second</li><li>third</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="Code-Grammar"><a href="#Code-Grammar" class="headerlink" title="Code Grammar"></a>Code Grammar</h2><h2 id="代码语法"><a href="#代码语法" class="headerlink" title="代码语法"></a>代码语法</h2><p>At the command prompt,type <code>nano</code>.<br><code>At the command prompt,type `nano`</code>.</p><h2 id="Code-Block"><a href="#Code-Block" class="headerlink" title="Code Block"></a><strong>Code Block</strong></h2><pre><code>&lt;html&gt;    &lt;head&gt;        &lt;title&gt;Test&lt;/title&gt;    &lt;/head&gt;</code></pre><p><strong>or <em>fenced code blocks</em>.</strong></p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;firstName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;John&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;lastName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;Smith&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;age&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="number">25</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Horizontal-Rule"><a href="#Horizontal-Rule" class="headerlink" title="Horizontal Rule"></a>Horizontal Rule</h2><h2 id="分割线"><a href="#分割线" class="headerlink" title="分割线"></a>分割线</h2><p>Try to put a blank line before…</p><hr><p>…and after a horizontal rule.</p><h2 id="Links-Grammar"><a href="#Links-Grammar" class="headerlink" title="Links Grammar"></a>Links Grammar</h2><h2 id="超链接语法"><a href="#超链接语法" class="headerlink" title="超链接语法"></a>超链接语法</h2><blockquote><p>This is a <em><strong><a href="https://github.com/" title="GitHub Offical Website">GitHub</a></strong></em> Link.  </p></blockquote><h2 id="网址URL"><a href="#网址URL" class="headerlink" title="网址URL"></a>网址URL</h2><h3 id="针对连接中有空格应该使用-20代替"><a href="#针对连接中有空格应该使用-20代替" class="headerlink" title="针对连接中有空格应该使用%20代替"></a>针对连接中有空格应该使用%20代替</h3><blockquote><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com/">https://www.baidu.com</a><br><a href="https://github.com/">https://github.com/</a><br><a href="https://www.example.com/my%20great%20page">link</a><br><code>https://github.com</code></p></blockquote><h2 id="应用类型连接"><a href="#应用类型连接" class="headerlink" title="应用类型连接"></a>应用类型连接</h2><p>[hobbit-hole][1]<br>[1]: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hobbit#Lifestyle">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hobbit#Lifestyle</a>  </p><blockquote><p>连接到<a href="#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95">代码语法</a></p></blockquote><h2 id="图片语法"><a href="#图片语法" class="headerlink" title="图片语法"></a>图片语法</h2><blockquote><p><img src="/2022/10/08/MarkDownLearning/farmer.png" alt="Farmer" title="This is a farmer"> </p></blockquote><pre><code>图片添加链接</code></pre><blockquote><p><a href="https://github.com/"><img src="/2022/10/08/MarkDownLearning/farmer.png" alt="Farmer"></a></p></blockquote><h2 id="转义字符语法"><a href="#转义字符语法" class="headerlink" title="转义字符语法"></a>转义字符语法</h2><ul><li><p>Without the backslash, this would be a bullet in an unordered list.</p><p>* Without the backslash, this would be a bullet in an unordered list.</p></li></ul><h2 id="内嵌-HTML-标签"><a href="#内嵌-HTML-标签" class="headerlink" title="内嵌 HTML 标签"></a>内嵌 HTML 标签</h2><p>This <strong>word</strong> is bold. This <em>word</em> is italic.  </p><h2 id="区块标签"><a href="#区块标签" class="headerlink" title="区块标签"></a>区块标签</h2><p>This is a regular paragraph.</p><table>    <tr>        <td>Foo</td>    </tr>    <p>This is a p test.</p></table><p>This is another regular paragraph.  </p><h2 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h2><blockquote><table><thead><tr><th align="left">列1</th><th align="center">列2</th><th align="right">列3</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">Header</td><td align="center">Title</td><td align="right">Name</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>halo</code></td><td align="center"><a href="https://github.com/">kitor</a></td><td align="right"><strong>ki</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote><h2 id="脚注"><a href="#脚注" class="headerlink" title="脚注"></a>脚注</h2><p>Here’s a simple footnote,[^1] and here’s a longer one.[^bignote]</p><p>[^1]: This is the first footnote.</p><p>[^bignote]: Here’s one with multiple paragraphs and code.</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Indent paragraphs to include them in the footnote.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">`&#123; my code &#125;`</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Add as many paragraphs as you like.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="标题编号连接"><a href="#标题编号连接" class="headerlink" title="标题编号连接"></a>标题编号连接</h2><!-- ### My Great Heading -->]]></content>
      
      
      
